dot_data = StringIO()
filename = "loptree.png"
featureNames = dataset_filter.columns[0:6]
targetNames = df["situacao"].unique().tolist()#dataset_filter["situacao"].unique().tolist()
out=tree.export_graphviz(LopTree,feature_names=featureNames, out_file=dot_data, class_names= np.unique(y_train), filled=True,  special_characters=True,rotate=False)  
graph = pydotplus.graph_from_dot_data(dot_data.getvalue())  
graph.write_png(filename)
img = mpimg.imread(filename)
plt.figure(figsize=(200, 200))
plt.imshow(img,interpolation='nearest')
